@startuml
title GRADES.RF001 - Lançar Nota

actor TEACHER

boundary Frontend
control GradeResolver
control GradeService
control GPAService
control NotificationService
control AuditService

database PostgreSQL

TEACHER -> Frontend : Seleciona turma

Frontend -> GradeResolver : mutation launchGrade(dto)

GradeResolver -> GradeService : launchGrade(dto)

GradeService -> PostgreSQL : validarProfessorTurma()

PostgreSQL --> GradeService : resultado

alt Professor autorizado

    GradeService -> PostgreSQL : validarAluno()

    alt Aluno existe

        GradeService -> PostgreSQL : verificarStatusAluno()

        alt Status = ACTIVE

            GradeService -> PostgreSQL : verificarMatricula()

            alt Matriculado na turma

                GradeService -> GradeService : validarNota(0-10)

                GradeService -> GradeService : validarPeso(>0)

                GradeService -> GradeService : validarData()

                GradeService -> PostgreSQL : salvarNota()

                PostgreSQL --> GradeService : notaPersistida

                GradeService -> GPAService : recalcularGPA(aluno)

                GPAService -> PostgreSQL : buscarNotasPeriodo()

                PostgreSQL --> GPAService : notas

                GPAService -> GPAService : calcularMediaPonderada()

                GPAService -> PostgreSQL : atualizarHistorico()

                GradeService -> NotificationService : enviarNotificacaoNota()

                NotificationService -> PostgreSQL : buscarEmails()

                NotificationService --> GradeService : email enviado

                GradeService -> AuditService : registrarEvento()

                AuditService --> GradeService : log salvo

                GradeService --> GradeResolver : Nota criada

                GradeResolver --> Frontend : HTTP 201

                Frontend --> TEACHER : Lançamento realizado

            else Não matriculado

                GradeService --> GradeResolver : Erro matrícula

                GradeResolver --> Frontend : HTTP 400

                Frontend --> TEACHER : Aluno não pertence à turma

            end

        else Status inválido

            GradeService --> GradeResolver : Erro Status

            GradeResolver --> Frontend : HTTP 400

            Frontend --> TEACHER : Aluno inativo

        end

    else Aluno inexistente

        GradeService --> GradeResolver : Aluno não encontrado

        GradeResolver --> Frontend : HTTP 404

        Frontend --> TEACHER : Erro

    end

else Professor sem permissão

    GradeResolver --> Frontend : HTTP 403

    Frontend --> TEACHER : Acesso negado

end

@enduml